{
  "id": "5b09f3bb691b8000147364d7",
  "title": "マッハ講義",
  "created": 1527378880,
  "updated": 1528383240,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5b09f3bb691b8000147364d7",
      "text": "マッハ講義",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1527378880,
      "updated": 1528355662
    },
    {
      "id": "5b09f3bfaff09e00009a9cad",
      "text": "\t大学の講義90分×8～12コマをゼロから設計するのは大変",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1527378880,
      "updated": 1527378934
    },
    {
      "id": "5b09f3f7aff09e00009a9caf",
      "text": "\tもっとリーンにやれないか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1527378936,
      "updated": 1527384499
    },
    {
      "id": "5b0a0abdaff09e0000a2507d",
      "text": "\t西尾の講義を聞きたいという人はいる(=見込み顧客がいる)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1527384766,
      "updated": 1527384778
    },
    {
      "id": "5b0a0acbaff09e0000a2507f",
      "text": " \t顧客が何を求めているかがわからない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1527384779,
      "updated": 1527384786
    },
    {
      "id": "5b0a0ad1aff09e0000a25080",
      "text": "  顧客に「あなたは何が欲しいですか」と聞いても正しい答えは得られない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1527384786,
      "updated": 1527384798
    },
    {
      "id": "5b0a0addaff09e0000a25081",
      "text": "  作って見せるしかない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1527384798,
      "updated": 1527384805
    },
    {
      "id": "5b0a09bbaff09e0000a25074",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1527384507,
      "updated": 1527384507
    },
    {
      "id": "5b13f4b3aff09e0000eb18a9",
      "text": " [マッハ新書]という[破壊的イノベーション]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1528034484,
      "updated": 1528034488
    },
    {
      "id": "5b13f4b9aff09e0000eb18aa",
      "text": " \tマッハ＝[思惟経済]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1528034491,
      "updated": 1528034491
    },
    {
      "id": "5b0a09b2aff09e0000a25073",
      "text": " \t「マッハ講義」という実験はどうか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1527384499,
      "updated": 1528034501
    },
    {
      "id": "5b13f4bcaff09e0000eb18ab",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1528034494,
      "updated": 1528034502
    },
    {
      "id": "5b09f3ccaff09e00009a9cae",
      "text": "\t「事前にしっかり計画して、それを実行する」ではない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1527378893,
      "updated": 1527384552
    },
    {
      "id": "5b0a09f6aff09e0000a25078",
      "text": " \t知識の獲得の重要度が高いシチュエーション",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1527384566,
      "updated": 1527384578
    },
    {
      "id": "5b0a0a04aff09e0000a25079",
      "text": "  なるべく早く顧客のフィードバックを得たい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1527384581,
      "updated": 1527384589
    },
    {
      "id": "5b13f553aff09e0000eb18ac",
      "text": "   [リーン・スタートアップ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1528034646,
      "updated": 1528034646
    },
    {
      "id": "5b0a09e8aff09e0000a25077",
      "text": "  \t小さくスタートし、素早くリリース",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1527384552,
      "updated": 1528034646
    },
    {
      "id": "5b0a0a2daff09e0000a2507b",
      "text": "    [アジャイル]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1527384622,
      "updated": 1528034652
    },
    {
      "id": "5b0a0a60aff09e0000a2507c",
      "text": "  \t\t[学習する組織]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1527384672,
      "updated": 1528034654
    },
    {
      "id": "5b13f567aff09e0000eb18ad",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1528034665,
      "updated": 1528034665
    },
    {
      "id": "5b13f568aff09e0000eb18ae",
      "text": " 過去の講義資料をいっぱいある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1528034665,
      "updated": 1528034675
    },
    {
      "id": "5b13f7e8aff09e0000eb18c9",
      "text": "  しかし講義資料をたくさん準備して話すスタイルでは、テレビのように一方的に聞く場になってしまう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1528035305,
      "updated": 1528035919
    },
    {
      "id": "5b13f856aff09e0000eb18d8",
      "text": "\t講義資料をたくさん用意して話すスタイル",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1528035415,
      "updated": 1528035415
    },
    {
      "id": "5b13f856aff09e0000eb18d9",
      "text": " \t話し手と聞き手の役割が分かれる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1528035415,
      "updated": 1528035415
    },
    {
      "id": "5b13f856aff09e0000eb18da",
      "text": "  テレビのように一方的に聞く場になる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1528035415,
      "updated": 1528035415
    },
    {
      "id": "5b13f578aff09e0000eb18b1",
      "text": "    対話をしたい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1528034681,
      "updated": 1528035325
    },
    {
      "id": "5b13f57baff09e0000eb18b2",
      "text": "    そこで資料は箇条書き程度しか準備しない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1528034685,
      "updated": 1528035325
    },
    {
      "id": "5b13f568aff09e0000eb18af",
      "text": "   結果として質疑の時間がたくさんになる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1528034665,
      "updated": 1528035325
    },
    {
      "id": "5b10d77caff09e000065eacd",
      "text": "   僕とのそういう時間に価値を感じる人の集まりにしたい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1527830396,
      "updated": 1528035325
    },
    {
      "id": "5b13fa9faff09e0000eb18ec",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1528036001,
      "updated": 1528036001
    },
    {
      "id": "5b13f904aff09e0000eb18dc",
      "text": "【本特別講義について】",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1528035590,
      "updated": 1528036002
    },
    {
      "id": "5b13f8e4aff09e0000eb18db",
      "text": "私は「エンジニアのための自分経営戦略」「エンジニアのための学ぶ技術」「学び方のデザイン」などいくつもの講演をしてきましたが、講義資料をたくさん用意して話すスタイルではどうしても「話し手」と「聞き手」に役割が分かれてしまい、テレビのように一方的に聞く場になってしまいがちです。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1528035558,
      "updated": 1528036003
    },
    {
      "id": "5b13f98daff09e0000eb18e6",
      "text": "そこで今回、あえて資料を箇条書き程度にしか準備せず、参加者との「対話」を重視するスタイルを採用しました。是非とも積極的に講義に参加し、講師との「対話」をお楽しみください。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1528035726,
      "updated": 1528036038
    },
    {
      "id": "5b13fb00aff09e0000eb18ed",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1528036097,
      "updated": 1528036097
    },
    {
      "id": "5b13fa39aff09e0000eb18e8",
      "text": "参考文献",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1528035899,
      "updated": 1528036099
    },
    {
      "id": "5b13fa14aff09e0000eb18e7",
      "text": "・MANABIYA基調講演「エンジニアのための自分経営戦略」 https://scrapbox.io/nishio/%E3%82%A8%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B8%E3%83%8B%E3%82%A2%E3%81%AE%E3%81%9F%E3%82%81%E3%81%AE%E8%87%AA%E5%88%86%E7%B5%8C%E5%96%B6%E6%88%A6%E7%95%A5",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1528035862,
      "updated": 1528036093
    },
    {
      "id": "5b13fa51aff09e0000eb18ea",
      "text": "・「エンジニアのための学ぶ技術」 https://www.slideshare.net/nishio/ss-54458355",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1528035923,
      "updated": 1528036095
    },
    {
      "id": "5b13fa51aff09e0000eb18eb",
      "text": "・京都大学サマーデザインスクール「学び方のデザイン」http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1528035923,
      "updated": 1528036096
    },
    {
      "id": "5b13f63faff09e0000eb18b5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1528034881,
      "updated": 1528035896
    },
    {
      "id": "5b13f6c6aff09e0000eb18ba",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1528035016,
      "updated": 1528035016
    },
    {
      "id": "5b13f64baff09e0000eb18b7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1528034892,
      "updated": 1528035412
    },
    {
      "id": "5b13f65aaff09e0000eb18b9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1528034907,
      "updated": 1528034907
    },
    {
      "id": "5b10d77baff09e000065eacc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1527830396,
      "updated": 1528034907
    },
    {
      "id": "5b10b51baff09e0000dafff8",
      "text": "-----",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1527821596,
      "updated": 1527821601
    },
    {
      "id": "5b10b520aff09e0000dafffa",
      "text": "[塩澤 一洋]先生の授業",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1527821601,
      "updated": 1527821610
    },
    {
      "id": "5b10b52baff09e0000dafffb",
      "text": "\tAppleTVをプロジェクターにつなぎ、iPadの画面ミラーリングで投影",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1527821612,
      "updated": 1527821640
    },
    {
      "id": "5b10b54aaff09e0000dafffc",
      "text": " \t自由に歩き回りまわることができ、資料に手書きで書きこむこともできる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1527821644,
      "updated": 1527821666
    },
    {
      "id": "5b10b55caff09e0000dafffd",
      "text": " ScrapboxとMetamoji Noteを4本指左右スワイプのアプリ切り替えで切り替えて使う",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1527821662,
      "updated": 1527821846
    },
    {
      "id": "5b10b615aff09e0000dafffe",
      "text": " Scrapboxに話す内容を箇条書きで書いておく",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1527821846,
      "updated": 1527821891
    },
    {
      "id": "5b10b642aff09e0000daffff",
      "text": " Metamoji Noteのレーザーポインター機能を良く使う",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1527821891,
      "updated": 1527821901
    },
    {
      "id": "5b18db5caff09e00005e7b40",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1528355676,
      "updated": 1528355676
    },
    {
      "id": "5b10b51baff09e0000dafff9",
      "text": " 90分の講義と12回の授業は違う",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1527821596,
      "updated": 1528355689
    },
    {
      "id": "5b18db7faff09e00005e7b43",
      "text": "  全く異なるスキル",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1528355711,
      "updated": 1528355716
    },
    {
      "id": "5b18db69aff09e00005e7b41",
      "text": "  情報を伝える場になりがち",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1528355690,
      "updated": 1528355701
    },
    {
      "id": "5b18db75aff09e00005e7b42",
      "text": "  成長に貢献する場にする",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1528355701,
      "updated": 1528355721
    },
    {
      "id": "5b18db88aff09e00005e7b44",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1528355721,
      "updated": 1528355722
    },
    {
      "id": "5b0a0ae9aff09e0000a25082",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1527384809,
      "updated": 1528383240
    },
    {
      "id": "5b0a0b2caff09e0000a25085",
      "text": "-----",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1527384876,
      "updated": 1527385813
    },
    {
      "id": "5b0a09dfaff09e0000a25076",
      "text": "\t顧客に「何が欲しいですか？」と聞いてみた結果",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1527384543,
      "updated": 1527384889
    },
    {
      "id": "5b0a0b38aff09e0000a25087",
      "text": "  一つは「AIって結局なんなの？」という疑問に答えるもの。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1527384889,
      "updated": 1527384891
    },
    {
      "id": "5b0a0b38aff09e0000a25088",
      "text": "  二つめは「社外で評価されるためにどう行動したのか」というもの。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1527384889,
      "updated": 1527384891
    },
    {
      "id": "5b0a0b38aff09e0000a25089",
      "text": "  三つめは「新任教授として東工大MOTにこんな価値を出していきたいのだけど、みなさんどう思います？」というもの。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1527384889,
      "updated": 1527384892
    },
    {
      "id": "5b0a0b2eaff09e0000a25086",
      "text": "\t\t二つめの社内で評価されなくて苦しかったところから始まる話は聴衆の激烈な共感が得られると思いますし、そこからどう考え行動していったのかというところは多くの人の感心があるところと思います",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1527384879,
      "updated": 1527384987
    },
    {
      "id": "5b0a0b80aff09e0000a2508a",
      "text": " ファン目線が強い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1527384960,
      "updated": 1527385013
    },
    {
      "id": "5b0a0bb6aff09e0000a2508c",
      "text": "  僕個人の「僕はこんな苦労を乗り越えました」みたいな話はあんまりしたくない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1527385014,
      "updated": 1527385022
    },
    {
      "id": "5b0a0bbfaff09e0000a2508d",
      "text": "  こういう提案があった時に喜んで乗っかって自分語りするタイプの人があまり好きではない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1527385024,
      "updated": 1527385052
    },
    {
      "id": "5b0a0bd9aff09e0000a2508e",
      "text": "\tしばらく話をして「知的生産術」はよいのではないかというとりあえずの案になった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1527385049,
      "updated": 1527385262
    },
    {
      "id": "5b0a0c9eaff09e0000a2508f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1527385246,
      "updated": 1527385246
    }
  ]
}